          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">Repair vs. replacement</p>
            <h2>When repair is appropriate</h2>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Isolated damage in a small section of the line</li>
              <li>Minor cracks or leaks at a single point</li>
              <li>Single blockage issues caused by a specific defect</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">Decision guide</p>
            <h2>When replacement is necessary</h2>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Aging pipes made of clay or Orangeburg materials</li>
              <li>Multiple problem areas across the system</li>
              <li>Frequent backups despite repeated repairs</li>
              <li>Bellied or collapsed pipes that cannot be relined</li>
              <li>Extensive root intrusion along the entire line length</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
